## Mission: Give taxpayers a direct say in how taxes are spent

## ##
## Requirements: ##
# Use Real ID to ensure 1 voice for each person
# Software capable of aggregating budget votes
# People should be able to visualize the Federal budget and make recommendations
# Frequency: not less than one year between votes, not more than four years
## ##

### Policy Recommendations ###
# Democratize federal budget - Citizens use Real ID access to make budget recommendations
    # For example: 20% Military, 30% Education, 15% support local law enforcement, 
    # 35% Healthcare - Insurance
# Budgets are allocated within +/- 5% threshold per voting.
# Voting occurs annually.
